==Mandarin==
===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' yī cù ér jiù)
# to reach the goal in one step; happen all at once
#* '''2004''' ''anon'', ''[http://hlj.rednet.com.cn/Articles/2004/11/639167.HTM 外汇管理局表示：人民币汇率改革不会一蹴而就]'' (Foreign Exchange Bureau announces: the [[renminbi|RMB]] exchange rate reforms will not '''happen all at once''')
#*: ''[[人民币]][[汇率]][[改革]][[不会]]'''一蹴而就'''.'' ([[Simplified Chinese|simplified]])
#*: ''[[人民幣]][[匯率]][[改革]][[不會]]'''一蹴而就'''.'' ([[Traditional Chinese|traditional]])
#*:: ''The [[renminbi|RMB]] exchange rate reforms will not '''happen all at once'''.

